Package org.hibernate.query.sqm.function

Class SqmFunctionRegistry

java.lang.Object
org.hibernate.query.sqm.function.SqmFunctionRegistry
public class SqmFunctionRegistry extends Object
Defines a registry for SqmFunctionDescriptor instances.

The SqmFunctionRegistry may be configured by a FunctionContributor.
